---
title: Chicken & Bacon Pesto Penne with Roasted Cherry Tomatoes
description: This pasta combines lots of favourites in a yummy bowl – with chicken breast, bacon, cherry tomatoes and pesto, it's sure to please the whole family. Plus there’s a secret addition of baby spinach – the tender strands melt into the sauce, adding flavour and goodness – but nobody will know!
